Rules (FINAL)
•	Student cannot:
o	Join same club twice
o	Enroll twice in same event
o	Enroll after event date
•	Leader:
o	Can manage only own club
•	Admin:
o	Full control
•	Event Lifecycle:
o	Pending → Approved
o	Past approved event → Completed (auto by date)
•	Cancel / Postpone lifecycle intentionally excluded

